title: User wants to receive error when placing player with submitted waiver request on 7 Day DL
custom_preconds:
GIVEN a user is logged in as a Club or BOC user
AND user is attempting to Submit a Place on 7 Day DL tx for a player
AND selected player has a submitted waiver request (Request Bulletin not yet sent) with Request Date on or after the Injury Date on the DL tx
custom_steps: WHEN user clicks "Submit" or "Approve" (all places OnSubmit rules are fired)
custom_expected:
THEN system should throw error "Player with a submitted waiver request may not be assigned. The waiver request should be deleted before re-submitting the assignment."
AND Clicking Back should close the modal and return user to the tx
AND clicking Ignore and Continue should ignore the error and continue with tx (BOC Only)

title: User wants to receive error when placing player who has previously secured waivers on 7 Day DL
custom_preconds:
GIVEN a user is logged in as a Club or BOC user
AND user is attempting to Submit a Place on 7 Day DL tx for a player
AND player has any secured waivers (waivers in effect on profile) as of the Injury Date
custom_steps: WHEN user clicks "Submit" or "Approve" (all places OnSubmit rules are fired)
custom_expected:
THEN system should throw error "Previously secured {0} waivers for this player will be cancelled as a result of this placement."
AND {0} should be replaced with the waiver type
AND Clicking Back should close the modal and return user to the tx
AND clicking Ignore and Continue should ignore the error and continue with tx

title: User wants to receive error when placing player who has any pending waiver requests on 7 Day DL
custom_preconds:
GIVEN a user is logged in as a Club or BOC user

custom_steps: WHEN user clicks "Submit" or "Approve" (all places OnSubmit rules are fired)
custom_expected:
THEN system should throw error "Player has pending {0} waiver request(s) that will be cancelled as a result of this placement."
AND {0} should be replaced with the waiver type
AND Clicking Back should close the modal and return user to the tx
AND clicking Ignore and Continue should ignore the error and continue with tx

title: User wants approving Place on 7-Day DL to cancel Player's Waivers
custom_preconds:
GIVEN a player has Waivers in effect
AND club or BOC user has created a Place on 7 Day DL tx for this player
AND Injury Date entered on the DL placement is AFTER Player's Waiver's Request Date
custom_steps: WHEN the Place on 7 Day DL tx reaches a status of Approved
custom_expected:
THEN player's in effect Waivers should be cancelled
AND Cancelled date and the Cancellation reason should be updated on the player profile
AND Cancellation reason on the profile should be set to - "Cancelled by DL Placement"
AND the waiver request result should be updated to "Cancelled on <date>"

title: User wants to see flags on 60 Day DL (MJ + MN) if certain rule checks fail
custom_preconds:
GIVEN a BOC user is logged in
AND user is viewing a submitted MN-Place on 60 Day DL tx with one or more flags set
custom_steps: WHEN user clicks the flags icon
custom_expected:
THEN system should open a popover with the flags that are currently set for the form
AND if assignment will result in the player's previously secured waivers being cancelled, then flag "Player's secured waivers will be cancelled with the approval of this transaction." should appear
AND if assignment will result in the player's pending waiver request(s) to be cancelled, then flag "Player's pending waiver requests will be cancelled with the approval of this transaction" should appear
AND if player's Injury Date matches the Claim Expire Date or the Withdrawal Date of a waiver, then flag "Player's Waiver may need to be cancelled with the approval of this transaction. "should appear
AND user should see these flags on the Approvals clipboard as well as on the form itself

title: User can view Disabled List history on Pro Player's Transaction Tab
custom_preconds: GIVEN a user is logged in as Club or BOC
custom_steps: WHEN user navigates to Transactions Tab on Pro Player's Profile
custom_expected:
THEN Disabled List section should be available on all professional player's Transactions tabs
AND available fields and layout of the section should match the provided wireframe
AND History should show one row per Approved, DL Placement and Transfer
AND Rehab and Recertification information should not display
AND History should be sorted in reverse chronological order
AND Date column should be the placement date from the transaction and should link to the transaction itself
AND Org/Club should match the Org/Club from the placement
AND DL Type should show the DL level they are being placed on or transferred to (7-Day, 15-Day, etc.)
AND Earliest Reinstatement Date should be populated from the transaction
AND Reinstatement should show the date the player was reinstated from the placement
AND  if player has not yet been reinstated, this column should be blank
AND Reason for Placement should follow the same logic as the "Injury" population does on the Reinstate from DL transaction
